===Etymology===
The two pronunciations are ultimately cognate, derived from a root meaning "to join, to come together ~ to meet, to gather ~ to match, to fit - to understand". Perhaps related to {{zh-l|合|to match}} ~ {{zh-l|蓋|lid}}.

Graphically: {{Han compound|亼|曾|ls=ic}} - a lid on top of an ancient double boiler.

